response.overview: Wet Lube mogul Max Grand promotes underling Sean Dickson to warehouse manager. Sean practices some Quality Control techniques on Anthony Mengetti with a quick lay in his office. Next, Max invites old flame Tom Katt to relight the fire over the hood of a Jaguar convertible. Then new employee Brent Cross joins the union between Joe Kent, Dax Kelly, and Eduardo on a truck's flatbed. Eduardo, Joe, and Dax continue the action atop a forklift. Finally, Max gives Adam Wilde a reason to walk bowlegged!
response.title: Wet Warehouse Part 2: Drenched
